AUDIO: 'we will focus on the unique strengths and weaknesses of this model Let\'s give it a relatively challenging task first Look the driving video hasn\'t changed But I replaced the image with a beautiful woman playing the guitar This image presents a certain challenge for the model'

[07:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'as she is holding a guitar Now let\'s look at the generated result: the movement migration is fine and the guitar hasn\'t disappeared Furthermore she interacts with the guitar very naturally'

[07:33] [scene:talk]
