AUDIO: 'I believe this highlights the model\'s powerful adaptability We can see that the final generated character given this pose and this image has a perspective consistent with the original image Do you think the character aligned to the pose'

[07:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'or the pose aligned to the character? I\'m sure you already know the answer: the pose aligned to the character This is exactly why we told you earlier that it is an I2V model where we align the pose to the character'

[07:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Of course this method is not without its drawbacks Look at this example: this character is seated Many people might think I\'m asking too much but since we are testing we should check all scenarios'

[08:12] [scene:talk]
